webpackJsonp([0xf9cd025687a5],{4872:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"We Got The Money",date:"14 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-14-we-got-the-money/",tags:"Y2007"},html:"<p>We got the money... and the papers, both yesterday.</p>\n<p>Our financing came through yesterday. The rate is pretty much the same as the first offer, but the small print is better (repayment begins later, less insurance required). Best of all, the extra funds for the Gym & Fun are included.</p>\n<p>We also got the notarized documents for the GmbH yesterday, which means we can register as a business *(Gewerbe)* with the city and start acting like a business, for example, open a bank account and start paying bills with company funds instead of our own.</p>\n<p>Unfortunately we've gotten some rejections from employees who don't want to continue with us when we take over, so we're going to be a little short staffed for the first month. We've already interviewed a trainee we'd like to hire, and we'd love to hire a couple of *Azubis* (apprentices... in Germany gastronomy is a recognized trade) to start in August. In the meantime Frauke and I will be spending a lot of time in the restaurant. She's pencilled herself in for 32 shifts in July.</p>"},next:{fields:{title:"Burger King Ignites Spam War With Rival",date:"11 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-11-burger-king-ignites-spam-war-with-rival/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Paper Weight",date:"15 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-15-paper-weight/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Burger King Ignites Spam War With Rival",date:"11 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-11-burger-king-ignites-spam-war-with-rival/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p><a href="http://us.rd.yahoo.com/finance/news/rss/story/*http://biz.yahoo.com/ap/070611/burger_king_spam.html?.v=4">Burger King Ignites Spam War With Rival</a>... it\'s not what you might think, unless you are a fan of <a href="http://spam.com/">spiced ham in a can</a>. :-)</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Birthday Present",date:"11 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-11-birthday-present/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"We Got The Money",date:"14 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-14-we-got-the-money/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Birthday Present",date:"11 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-11-birthday-present/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>MamaMaus has her birthday today, and Christopher wanted to make her something special, something for the new restaurant. He decided on an "M" logo for her office... sure, she can get plenty of logos, but how many of them are hand-painted?</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/540319606/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://farm2.static.flickr.com/1080/540319606_015a045316.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG_2062" /></a></p>\n<p>We made all the preparations on Saturday. We had to buy the cardboard, a tube of yellow paint, and a artist\'s palette. And since Mama has offices both at home and at work, he had to of course create two.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/540319732/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://farm2.static.flickr.com/1400/540319732_673b10e89d.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG_2063" /></a></p>\n<p>I was more practical in my gift selection. To help us adjust to our new lifestyle, I found a some books:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://www.amazon.de/Kunst-stilvollen-Verarmens-ohne-reich/dp/3499616688/ref=pd_bbs_sr_1/302-5032874-9994428?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1181556096&amp;sr=8-1" title="Die Kunst des stilvollen Verarmens. Wie man ohne Geld reich wird">Die Kunst des stilvollen Verarmens. Wie man ohne Geld reich wird</a> (The Art of Stylishly Becoming Poorer: How to Become Rich Without Money) </li>\n<li><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Our-Iceberg-Melting-Succeeding-Conditions/dp/031236198X/ref=pd_bbs_sr_2/105-2606337-0531609?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1181556897&amp;sr=8-2" title="Our Iceberg Is Melting: Changing and Succeeding Under Any Conditions">Our Iceberg Is Melting: Changing and Succeeding Under Any Conditions</a>. </li>\n<li>Plus a book on Feng-Shui, to make sure we don\'t make any fatal mistakes when designing the McCaf√©.</li>\n</ul>'},next:{fields:{title:"Fashion for the Children of Heiligendamm",date:"04 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-04-fashion-for-the-children-of-heiligendamm/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Burger King Ignites Spam War With Rival",date:"11 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-11-burger-king-ignites-spam-war-with-rival/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:121,pageCount:1101}}}});
